# simple test of fcc Cu with ACE recursive

units           metal
atom_style      atomic

neighbor        0.3 bin
neigh_modify    every 2 delay 10 check yes

read_data       Cu_disturbed.lmp  

pair_style      pace recursive
pair_coeff  * * Cu-PBE-core-rep.ace Cu

timestep        0.001
fix             1 all nve

thermo          5
thermo_style    custom step temp pe ke

run             2

